The Coca-Cola Company - Wikipedia






















 






The Coca-Cola Company

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the company. For the carbonated beverage, see Coca-Cola.





This article may have been created or substantially edited in return for undisclosed payments, a violation of Wikipedia's terms of use. Its neutrality may be compromised as a result. It may require cleanup to comply with Wikipedia's content policies, particularly neutral point of view and sourcing. Please discuss further on the talk page. (December 2016) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)



The Coca-Cola Company





Coca-Cola's corporate headquarters in Atlanta, Georgia, United States




